page_title: Quickstart: Use the OpenAI Service via PowerShell
page_description: Walkthrough on how to get started with Azure OpenAI and make your first completions call with PowerShell.
chunk_content: Prerequisites- An Azure subscription - Create one for free- You can use either the latest version, PowerShell 7, or Windows PowerShell 5.1.- An Azure OpenAI Service resource with a model deployed. For more information about model deployment, see the resource deployment guide.> [!div class="nextstepaction"]> I ran into an issue with the prerequisites.
